  "prompt": "How is work life balance in wipro consumer care and lighting?",
  "response": "Work-life balance at Wipro Consumer Care and Lighting can vary based on individual roles, team dynamics, and personal experiences. Generally, Wipro, as a large multinational corporation, promotes various initiatives aimed at maintaining a healthy work-life balance, such as flexible working hours, remote work options, and wellness programs.\n\nEmployee experiences, however, may differ. Some employees might appreciate the flexibility and supportive policies, while others might face challenges due to workload or project deadlines. Company culture, management support, and team structure can also influence how work-life balance is perceived.\n\nFor the most accurate insights, it's a good idea to check employee reviews on platforms like Glassdoor or seek firsthand accounts from current or former employees.",
